graph TD
    subgraph Tiers[Escalation Tiers]
        T1[Tier 1: Mandatory<br>Irreversible impact<br>e.g., Capital commitment, external communication]
        T2[Tier 2: Advisory<br>Significant impact<br>e.g., Data anomalies, thesis conflicts]
        T3[Tier 3: Informational<br>Awareness<br>e.g., Status updates, completed deliverables]
        T1 --- T2 --- T3
    end

    subgraph SenRef[SenRef Cycle Phases]
        S[Sense]
        M[Model]
        D[Decide]
        R[Reflect]
    end

    S -->|Mostly| T3
    M -->|When conflicts detected| T2
    D -->|Escalation concentration| T1
    D --> T2
    R -->|Proposing updates| T3
